title: SEMA Ignited 2015 - Valyrian Steel Burning Man Vehicle
description: Commissioned by artist Henry Chang, the Valyrian Steel vehicle was custom-built for Burning Man.  Handmade from steel tubing and powered by a Ford Coyote 5.0L engine,  this vehicle rolls on 54" Mickey Thompson tires in the rear, supported by Fox Shocks all around.
tags: SEMA 2015, SEMA, SEMA Ignited 2015, Valyrian Steel, Burning Man
